        </details>

        <details style="margin:1rem 0; padding:0.8rem; background:#fafafa; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #eee;">
          <summary style="cursor:pointer; font-weight:bold; color:#0b2c45;">Do I need both Part A and Part B?</summary>
